properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

parameters.name: targetObject
parameters.description: The document the process should inspect.

parameters.name: appliedProfile
parameters.description: The preflight profile that should be used.

parameters.name: preflightOptions
parameters.description: The preflight options that should be used. (Optional)

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.description: Initial values for properties of the new PreflightProcess (Optional)

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the PreflightProcess.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the PreflightProcess with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.name: itemByRange
methods.description: Returns the PreflightProcesses within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The PreflightProcess, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: PreflightProcess, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The PreflightProcess, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: PreflightProcess, Long Integer or String.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first PreflightProcess in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last PreflightProcess in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle PreflightProcess in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem
methods.description: Returns the PreflightProcess with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the PreflightProcess that follows the desired PreflightProcess.

methods.name: nextItem
methods.description: Returns the PreflightProcess whose index follows the specified PreflightProcess in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The PreflightProcess whose index comes before the desired PreflightProcess.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any PreflightProcess in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
methods.description: Returns every PreflightProcess in the collection.

methods.name: toSource
methods.description: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the PreflightProcess.
Returns the PreflightProcess with the specified index.
